  "detailed_description": "Code Tracer is a simple puzzle game.<br>You only have to cut codes, but be careful about time and electricity.<br><br><u>The tension of playing with a limited amount of time</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/fea5f34c5527ea44284ac7a6df85ef39.poster.avif?t=1593083645\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/fea5f34c5527ea44284ac7a6df85ef39.webm?t=1593083645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/fea5f34c5527ea44284ac7a6df85ef39.mp4?t=1593083645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's a tense game that requires you to make quick and<br>appropriate movements within a limited amount of time.<br><br><u>Medal system</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/c6fc13b977482d807cbb8b970cc875cf.poster.avif?t=1593083645\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/c6fc13b977482d807cbb8b970cc875cf.webm?t=1593083645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>You can earn medals according to your score,<br>and you can unlock stages with medals.<br><br><u>The boss stage is not a straightforward one</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/ba49ede3498ca835707d1f5edc429734.poster.avif?t=1593083645\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/ba49ede3498ca835707d1f5edc429734.webm?t=1593083645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155390/extras/ba49ede3498ca835707d1f5edc429734.mp4?t=1593083645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
